name: identifier
label: Identifier
description: A unique proper name or character sequence that identifies this particular metabolomics assay. (NCIT:C171266 )

name: belongsmetabolomicmaterialprocessing
label: Belongs metabolomic material processing
description: This metabolomic assay is part of a metabolomic material processing. (SIO:000068 )

name: assaytype
label: Assay type
description: Spectrometry where the sample is converted into gaseous ions which are characterised by their mass-to-charge ratio and relative abundance. (CHMO:0000470 )

name: inlet
label: Inlet
description: A valve that controls the flow of fluids in through the wall of a chamber. (NCIT:C50251 )

name: massspectrometer
label: Mass spectrometer
description: A piece of apparatus that consists of at least an ion source, a mass-to-charge analyser, a detector and a vacuum system and is used to measure mass spectra. (CHMO:0000982 )

name: ionizationsource
label: Ionization source
description: A piece of apparatus that takes an analyte and generates ions which are passed to the rest of a mass spectrometer for analysis. (CHMO:0000960 )

name: chromatographycolumn
label: Chromatography column
description: A piece of apparatus that has the form of a tube with a diameter between 5 to 50 mm and hosts the stationary bed in chromatography. (CHMO:0000997 )

name: phaseseparationprotocol
label: Phase separation protocol
description: Any method for the synthesis of polymer membranes that involves the polymer transforming from the liquid phase of the cast solution to the solid phase. (CHMO:0002214 )

name: massspecsourceconditions
label: Mass spec source conditions
description: Condition in which variables of the experiment are manipulated to determine the variables effect by comparing to a control condition. (ZECO:0000104 )
